(332, 1, '2020-11-28 09:18:13', '2020-11-28 09:18:13', '<p class=\"description-item-number\">ITEM#: 13747559</p>\r\nPrepare sauces and soups with ease using this Hamilton Beach food processor. Built with a wide mouth, this unit fits full-sized veggies to reduce chopping. The 500-watt motor powers through tough ingredients, and the two included bowls make it easy to prepare large and small servings.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cord Length: More than 1 ft.</li>\r\n 	<li>Display: Manual</li>\r\n 	<li>Removable Blade</li>\r\n 	<li>Material: Plastic</li>\r\n 	<li>Capacity: 12-Cup</li>\r\n 	<li>Number of Overall Speed: 3</li>\r\n 	<li>Speed Control Type: Button</li>\r\n 	<li>Size: Full Size</li>\r\n 	<li>Color: Black, Stainless Steel</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Hamilton Beach Big Mouth Dual Bowl Food Processor – Black', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'hamilton-beach-big-mouth-dual-bowl-food-processor-black', '', '', '2020-11-28 09:18:16', '2020-11-28 09:18:16', '', 0, 'http://localhost/kitchencorner/?post_type=product&#038;p=332', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(333, 1, '2020-11-28 09:19:50', '2020-11-28 09:19:50', '<p class=\"description-item-number\">ITEM#: 35287246</p>\r\nThis is our high quality and stylish food stand mixer which is great for your kitchen. It comes with dough hook and 6.3 QT stainless steel bowl. With 660 watt motor and 6 adjustable speeds guarantee that you can completely control your food stand mixer for perfect results. It is specially designed to whip up cakes, cookies, and creams with ease. It is easy to clean to make your kitchen tidy and orderly.\r\n\r\n<b>Note:The dough hook and mixer blade are made of cast aluminium, They are light and sturdy, but can’t wash in dishwasher. Or they will be oxidized.</b>\r\n<b>Features</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li> Easy to access the bowl because of tilting head design with easy-to-control knobs</li>\r\n 	<li>Capacity of 6.3 quarts is large enough to meet your daily demand</li>\r\n 	<li>3 different useful accessories, perfect for all types of food mixes</li>\r\n 	<li>6 speed settings for you control your food mixer easily</li>\r\n 	<li>Splash guards are perfect for keeping the kitchen tidy and clean</li>\r\n 	<li>Handle design makes it easy to move the bowl</li>\r\n 	<li>Non-slip suction feet, ideal for keeping the mixer stable</li>\r\n 	<li>Overheat protection setting, automatic stop when overheat</li>\r\n 	<li>360 -deg three-dimensional stirring design can achieve uniform stirring</li>\r\n 	<li>Blue LED lights add elegance to the product</li>\r\n 	<li>ETL certification ensures safety and high quality</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>Specifications</b>\r\nColor: Red/ White/ Sliver /BlackMaterial: ABS + Stainless Steel\r\nNet Weight: 11.5lbs\r\nVoltage: 120V, 60Hz\r\nPower: 660W\r\nProduct Dimensions: 15″ x 9.5″ x 13″(L x W x H)\r\nPackage includes:\r\n1 x Stand Mixer\r\n1 x Mixing Bowl\r\n1 x Dough Hook\r\n1 x Beater\r\n1 x Whisk\r\n1 x Splash Guard\r\n1 x User Manual', '6.3Qt Electric Tilt-Head Food Stand Mixer 6 Speed 660W – 6.3 Quart', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '6-3qt-electric-tilt-head-food-stand-mixer-6-speed-660w-6-3-quart', '', '', '2020-11-28 09:19:52', '2020-11-28 09:19:52', '', 0, 'http://localhost/kitchencorner/?post_type=product&#038;p=333', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(334, 1, '2020-11-28 09:21:32', '2020-11-28 09:21:32', '<p class=\"description-item-number\">ITEM#: 18626956</p>\r\nServe up savory grilled meals in every season with this indoor grill. Made with removable, dishwasher-safe plates for easy cleanup, this grill features a lid window so you can keep an eye on your food.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Indoor Searing Grill</li>\r\n 	<li>Window lets you watch food as it cooks</li>\r\n 	<li>Removable nonstick plate and dip tray are dishwasher safe</li>\r\n 	<li>High searing temperatures locks in juices and flavor</li>\r\n 	<li>Ready Indicator Light with adjustable temperature control</li>\r\n 	<li>Display: Manual</li>\r\n 	<li>Material: Cast Aluminum, Metal, Stainless Steel</li>\r\n 	<li>Color: Stainless Steel</li>\r\n 	<li>Dimensions: 18.13 inches x 10.63 inches x 14.31 inches</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Hamilton Beach Indoor Searing Grill with Lid Window', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'hamilton-beach-indoor-searing-grill-with-lid-window', '', '', '2020-11-28 09:21:35', '2020-11-28 09:21:35', '', 0, 'http://localhost/kitchencorner/?post_type=product&#038;p=334', 0, 'product', '', 0),
