(336, 1, '2020-11-28 09:24:13', '2020-11-28 09:24:13', '<p class=\"description-item-number\">ITEM#: 36930479</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>PowerXL Vortex 1500W 5qt 7-in-1 Digital Air Fryer w/Presets</h3>\r\n<strong>Shipping is Free!</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Description:</strong>\r\n\r\nGive this compact cuisine machine a home on your counter and deliver the crispy, crunchy goods in minutes –from fries to chicken tenders to pizza — using little to no oil. Now that sounds like a win-win thanks to the PowerXL 5-qt digital air fryer! From PowerXL.\r\n\r\n<strong>Features:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Includes 5-qt air fryer and inner fry tray</li>\r\n 	<li>1,500W total power</li>\r\n 	<li>Digital touchscreen LED display with time/temperature controls</li>\r\n 	<li>Adjustable temperature from 90F to 400F</li>\r\n 	<li>10 preset functions: French fries, roast, bake, shrimp, fish, chicken, steak, pizza, reheat, and dehydrate</li>\r\n 	<li>Dishwasher-safe parts</li>\r\n 	<li>Approximate measurements: Fryer 15.2″ x 11.3″ x 13.5″; weighs 9 lbs, 4.1 oz; Cord 47.24″L</li>\r\n 	<li>UL listed</li>\r\n 	<li>Imported<strong>Shipping Is FREE!</strong>\r\nAnywhere in the 48 States\r\n<strong>Shipping is Free!</strong></li>\r\n</ul>', 'PowerXL Vortex 1500W 5qt 7-in-1 Digital Air Fryer w/Presets', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'powerxl-vortex-1500w-5qt-7-in-1-digital-air-fryer-w-presets', '', '', '2020-11-28 09:24:15', '2020-11-28 09:24:15', '', 0, 'http://localhost/kitchencorner/?post_type=product&#038;p=336', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(337, 1, '2020-11-28 09:25:52', '2020-11-28 09:25:52', '<p class=\"description-item-number\">ITEM#: 14939006</p>\r\nOrganize oversize pans and cutting boards easily with this countertop cutting board wire organizer. Crafted from platinum-finished metal, this organizer features three wide wire slots over a mesh rack, creating small-footprint storage for your cooking supplies. The raised, ventilated base keeps boards and pans dry in case of spills.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dimensions: 10.25″ Dx 8″ x 5.5″ H</li>\r\n 	<li>Sturdy iron construction</li>\r\n 	<li>Great for organizing cutting boards, cookie sheets and skillets</li>\r\n 	<li>Elegant platinum finish</li>\r\n 	<li>Ventilated base</li>\r\n 	<li>Props in the image not included</li>\r\n 	<li>Weight:  2.15 lbs</li>\r\n 	<li>Item #: SHE14050B</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Seville Classic Kitchen Cabinet & Counter Top Cutting Board Organizer', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'seville-classic-kitchen-cabinet-counter-top-cutting-board-organizer', '', '', '2020-11-28 09:25:55', '2020-11-28 09:25:55', '', 0, 'http://localhost/kitchencorner/?post_type=product&#038;p=337', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(338, 1, '2020-11-28 09:26:57', '2020-11-28 09:26:57', '<p class=\"description-item-number\">ITEM#: 36749746</p>\r\nHold the most indispensable utensils and condiments in style with this mesh utensil and condiment caddy\r\n\r\nThe Essentials Held At Your Fingertips The YBM Home Utensil Caddy and Napkin Holder is the perfect addition to the kitchen to serve and display your everyday utensils in an organized pattern. This attractive mesh cutlery caddy offers a distinct approach to cluttered silverware drawers by keeping your flatware upright and readily available. Designed with one large and three small compartments with a handle to move it from place to place, this caddy is also multi-purpose to hold appetizing sauces for hot dogs, seasonings for BBQ, cups, bottles,; we’ve seen it used to store office supplies, classroom supplies, beauty products, personal care products, crafts, gadget accessories, coffee/tea/hot chocolate bags. The sky’s the limit.\r\n\r\nExcellent for Indoor and Outdoor Entertaining Without any distinction, this decorative tabletop accessory infuses aesthetically with any kitchen setting. If you are hosting a cookout in your backyard, this caddy conveniently makes things easy to carry altogether from the kitchen to the patio. For camping trips, fill it up with tomato bottles, mayonnaise, and disposable flatware for easy meal preparation.\r\n\r\nAttractive Design Upscale the Looks of Dining Table This caddy is made with high quality stainless steel and black or silver coating finish for a modern blending statement. The sturdiness and smart craftsmanship ensures long lasting durability. Measures approximately 7 in. W x 9.25 in. L x 4.375 in. Depth.\r\n\r\nHosting large parties? Add multiple caddies for convenience.', 'Mesh Condiment Caddy / Kitchen Supply, Utensil, Napkin Holder, 1151mb', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'mesh-condiment-caddy-kitchen-supply-utensil-napkin-holder-1151mb', '', '', '2020-11-28 09:27:00', '2020-11-28 09:27:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/kitchencorner/?post_type=product&#038;p=338', 0, 'product', '', 0);
