(339, 1, '2020-11-28 09:28:06', '2020-11-28 09:28:06', '<p class=\"description-item-number\">ITEM#: 28464891</p>\r\n23 PIECE SET Cooking Utensils Set in 2 Colors.\r\n\r\nStainless Steel Utensils Set For Heat Resistant Cooking.\r\n\r\nOne Complete Nylon set that provides you with every gadget that you need for a perfect cooking.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Made of nylon, plastic and stainless steel</li>\r\n 	<li>Available in Black &amp; Grey color</li>\r\n 	<li>Heat resistant to 450 degrees F</li>\r\n 	<li>Safe for all cookware types</li>\r\n 	<li>Dishwasher safe (except can opener)</li>\r\n 	<li>Dimensions: 17 inches long x 6 inches wide x 9 inches high</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>The ultimate 23 piece Kitchen Utensils set</strong> – One Complete Nylon set that supplies you with every kitchen utensils tool and gadget that you need for a perfect cooking utensils set.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Strong construction</strong>– Strong and Durable best Cooking utensils with Non-Stick Nylon heads that do not harm or leave marks on any of your non-stick cookware pans and pots unlike other plastic kitchen utensils. Lux Decor kitchen supplies are lightweight as well as tough making your cooking experience even better.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Sturdy handles</strong> – The handles of our kitchen tool set are made with 100% Stainless Steel which provide durability and strength as well as comfort that is not available in utensils with plastic handles.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Heat resistant</strong> – Each utensil from our cooking utensil set is safe to be used on all cookware as they are heat resistant.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Easy to clean</strong> – All utensils are dishwasher safe. Hannah Kitchen gadgets set uses Premium food grade silicone that is high temperature resistant and meets strict FDA and LFGB standards. All components are to be dried and stored.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>What’s in the Box?</strong></li>\r\n 	<li>Solid Spoon</li>\r\n 	<li>Solid Turner</li>\r\n 	<li>Ladle</li>\r\n 	<li>Pizza C