(340, 1, '2020-11-28 09:29:22', '2020-11-28 09:29:22', '<p class=\"description-item-number\">ITEM#: 37091674</p>\r\nThe MegaChef 14 Piece Silicone and Stainless Steel Kitchen Utensil Set is perfect for safe and healthy cooking. Don’t worry about scratching your expensive cookware, the silicone set will allow you to mix, scoop, flip and whisk scratch free. Food grade silicone is safe for all your family and friends. Durable and more sanitary, which prevents from chipping, warping, melting, rusting or damages. Also easy to clean, withstanding high temperatures, utensil set is dishwasher safe.', 'MegaChef 14Pc Gray Silicone and Stainless Steel Kitchen Utensil Set', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'megachef-14pc-gray-silicone-and-stainless-steel-kitchen-utensil-set', '', '', '2020-11-28 09:29:25', '2020-11-28 09:29:25', '', 0, 'http://localhost/kitchencorner/?post_type=product&#038;p=340', 0, 'product', '', 0),
